# Tailwind CSS Guide

Tailwind CSS is a utility-first CSS framework that enables rapid UI development with pre-built utility classes.

## Core Concepts

### Utility-First Approach
```html
<!-- Tailwind utility-first approach -->
<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Title</h2>
</div>
```

