## Responsive Design

Mobile-first breakpoints:
- `sm:` - 640px and up
- `md:` - 768px and up
- `lg:` - 1024px and up
- `xl:` - 1280px and up

```html
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
<h1 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-6xl">Responsive heading</h1>
<div class="hidden lg:block">Desktop only</div>
```

